These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, hot-chocolate, cola, sprite, milk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, water-polo, rugby, climbing, baseball
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is parkour##2
5. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is surfing##2
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking water##1
9. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | water | milk | sprite | cola    | hot-chocolate  |
| Sport   | baseball | surfing   | rugby       | climbing        | parkour | water-polo |

