.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, punk, hip-hop, dubstep, d&b, house
The people have 6 different jobs:  paramedic, freelancer, accountant, engineer, architect, security-guard
1. the engineer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the architect is on the left of the fan d&b##1
3. the engineer is between the fan dubstep and the fan techno##2
4. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the freelancer##1
5. the fan techno is on the far right##1
6. the architect is on the right of the security-guard##1
7. the fan dubstep is on the right of the paramedic##1
8. the fan punk is on the left of the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | punk | house | d&b | dubstep | hip-hop | techno  |
| Job           | security-guard | architect  | paramedic | freelancer    | engineer  | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, coffee, milk, water, lemonade
6 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, billiard, chess, domino, mah-jongg
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking water is between the person drinking milk and the person playing snooker##2
7. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Beverage         | cola | fanta | lemonade      | water | milk | coffee      |
| Game   | backgammon    | mah-jongg  | snooker | chess   | domino       | billiard |

