.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
House: tower, craftsman, farmhouse, townhouse, colonial, art-deco
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, rowing, sailing, swimming, parkour
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the townhouse house##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is the craftsman house##1
5. the tower house is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the art-deco house##2
7. the craftsman house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| House        | craftsman    | art-deco | farmhouse | tower | colonial | townhouse   |
| Sport   | sailing | swimming        | soccer  | biathlon     | parkour  | rowing |

