.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
City: berlin, hamburg, nizza, hannover, new-york, prague
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, february, march, august, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person traveling to prague##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in january##2
9. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| City    | berlin | prague | new-york  | hannover      | nizza | hamburg  |
| Birthday   | february  | march    | august | july | june | january |

