.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: rose, daffodil, lily, zinnia, bellflower, iris
The people have 6 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman, designer, journalist, manager, photographer
1. the journalist is the journalist##1
2. the photographer is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the person who growszinnia is the photographer##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is between the journalist and the manager##2
7. the journalist is on the right of the project-manager##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the journalist##1
9. the fisherman is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Flower       | iris | zinnia | rose | bellflower | lily | daffodil |
| Job   | designer | photographer    | manager  | project-manager    | journalist    | fisherman    |

