.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, cain, alhambra, bolivar, game, tiparillo
There are 6 different nationalities: polish, german, japanese, indonesian, turkish, french
1. the japanese is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the german##1
3. the french is between the turkish and the polish##2
4. the bolivar-smoker is the japanese##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the game-smoker##2
6. the polish is on the left of the french##1
7. the game-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the game-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
9. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Cigar           | bolivar | tiparillo | game | alhambra | cain | blend |
| Nationality   | japanese   | indonesian   | german         | polish    | french     | turkish     |

