.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, musical, sports, superhero, western, animation
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, helicopter, roller, snowmobile, taxi, ship
 1. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person driving the train is between the person watching romance movies and the person driving the ship##2
 3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | western  | musical | superhero | animation | sports     |
| Transport   | helicopter | train | ship    | taxi | snowmobile | roller |

