 1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the french##2
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the french##1
 8. the japanese is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the canadian is between the person watching superhero movies and the british##2
10. the japanese is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
