The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, december, august, october, january, july
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking milk and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person drinking juice##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Beverage           | almond-milk      | milk | hot-chocolate | juice   | coffee  | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | october | april  | december             | july | august | january       |

