.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: thriller, family, animation, western, superhero, comedy
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, milk, iced-tea, mirinda, cola
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the person watching family movies##2
 3. the person drinking mirinda is between the person watching comedy movies and the person drinking juice##2
 4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is between the person drinking milk and the person watching animation movies##2
 6. the person watching western movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | thriller | superhero   | animation     | comedy       | family       |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea   | juice | mirinda | cola | milk |

