.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, august, june, february, july, october
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, thriller, western, action, adventure, epic
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |       5       |   6    |
