.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, june, october, april, january, july
6 different pets are kept: pony, horse, goat, turtle, hedgehog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
5. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's birthday is in january and the owner of the turtle##2
8. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the pony##1
9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |   6   |
| Birthday   | april | december | october | january      | july | june |
| Pet     | pony   | turtle | guinea-pig     | goat | hedgehog  | horse   |

