.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-19::.
There 6 different types of food: peach, peas, pear, pineapple, radish, cucumber
6 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, rat, guinea-pig, ferret, turtle
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating pear##1
4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating radish##1
5. the person eating pineapple is the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating pineapple##2
7. the person eating peach is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rat##2
8. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |         2          |   3    |     4      |       5        |     6     |
| Food   | pear | peach             | cucumber  | radish        | peas       | pineapple    |
| Pet        | guinea-pig    | turtle | rat | hedgehog | ferret | bird |

